Package: dfdb.RSQLite
Type: Package
Title: Access Data Tables in a SQLite Data Base as Pseudo-Dataframes
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2009-12-01
Author: Oswaldo Cruz and John Fox
Maintainer: John Fox <jfox@mcmaster.ca>
Depends: RSQLite, DBI
Description: This package contains functions that allow the user to treat data
  tables in a SQLite-accessible data base as if they were data frames, including
  the ability to access subsets of the rows and columns of the table; 
  row "subscripts" can be specified as SQL queries.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
